            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-02/us.jpg?VersionId=0nWDQhLVaLVG1ibHSJP29ka6fbOkqi02&amp;itok=5SF7Xpkv" title="美国海军一架P-8A海神式（P-8 Poseidon）巡逻机飞越台湾海峡。（美军印太司令部官网档案照）" alt="美国海军一架P-8A海神式（P-8 Poseidon）巡逻机飞越台湾海峡。（美军印太司令部官网档案照）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-02/us.jpg?VersionId=0nWDQhLVaLVG1ibHSJP29ka6fbOkqi02&amp;itok=5SF7Xpkv" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
